% ==========================================================================
% TRIANGLE DESIGN
% Fills the slide with a low-poly mosaic of randomized triangles. Each 1cm
% square cell is subdivided into 4 triangles with independent random shading
% (±5% of the base color), creating a subtle faceted texture. The seed is
% fixed so output is reproducible across compiles.
%
% A single parameterized command handles all three pattern roles — pass a
% color and it handles full-color, light, and block variants alike. This
% makes it trivial to extend to new colors without additional commands.
% ==========================================================================

